title: All Along the Washed Hour by Jimi Trendrix 3/26: Echo Park, Suicide Squad, Dominion, Ronda Rousey
itunes:title: All Along the Washed Hour by Jimi Trendrix 3/26: Echo Park, Suicide Squad, Dominion, Ronda Rousey
description:
On this edition of All Along the Washed Hour by Jimi Trendrix Jack and Miles discuss the LAPD shutting down Echo Parks homeless encampment, the new Suicide Squad trailer, Dominion Voting Systems suing Fox News for defamation, and Ronda Rousey being a strong black woman.
